---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import SEOHead from '../../components/SEOHead.astro';
import Navbar from '../../components/Navbar.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
---

<BaseLayout>
  <SEOHead slot="head" title="Digital Waiver for Tattoo Shop — Paperless Consent Forms | InkFlow" description="Replace paper waivers with a digital tattoo consent form app. E-signatures, QR check-in, medical tracking. Clients sign on their phone before arrival. Start free." />
  <Navbar />

  <!-- HERO: Problem-first -->
  <section class="pt-24 pb-16 sm:pt-32">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-accent-400 mb-3">DIGITAL TATTOO CONSENT FORM APP</p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-white sm:text-5xl">Stop Hunting for Lost Waivers. Go Paperless in One Day.</h1>
      <p class="mt-6 text-lg text-gray-400">Replace clipboards and paper stacks with a digital waiver workflow. Clients sign on their phone before arrival. Every form stored, searchable, legally binding.</p>
      <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-4">
        <a href="https://app.ink-flows.com/register" class="inline-block rounded-lg bg-accent-500 px-8 py-3.5 text-base font-semibold text-ink-950 hover:bg-accent-400 transition-all">Try InkFlow Free →</a>
        <a href="/blog/how-to-digitize-tattoo-waivers" class="inline-block rounded-lg border border-ink-700 px-8 py-3.5 text-base font-semibold text-white hover:bg-ink-800 transition-all">Read the Guide</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- STATS -->
  <section class="border-t border-ink-800/50 py-12">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8 text-center">
        <div><p class="text-3xl font-bold text-accent-400">5min → 30s</p><p class="mt-1 text-sm text-gray-500">Check-in time reduction</p></div>
        <div><p class="text-3xl font-bold text-accent-400">100%</p><p class="mt-1 text-sm text-gray-500">Legally binding e-signatures</p></div>
        <div><p class="text-3xl font-bold text-accent-400">Zero</p><p class="mt-1 text-sm text-gray-500">Lost forms with cloud storage</p></div>
        <div><p class="text-3xl font-bold text-accent-400">Built-in</p><p class="mt-1 text-sm text-gray-500">Conditional medical logic</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- PROBLEM: Why paper fails -->
  <section class="border-t border-ink-800/50 py-16">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white text-center">Paper Waivers Are Costing You More Than You Think</h2>
      <div class="mt-8 space-y-4">
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-ink-800 bg-ink-900/30 p-5"><p class="text-gray-400"><strong class="text-white">⏱ 5 minutes per check-in</strong> — Finding the right form, cleaning the iPad, waiting for handwritten signatures. Multiply by 10 clients a day = nearly an hour lost.</p></div>
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-ink-800 bg-ink-900/30 p-5"><p class="text-gray-400"><strong class="text-white">🔍 "Where's last year's waiver?"</strong> — Paper files get lost, misfiled, or damaged. When a legal question comes up, you spend hours hunting.</p></div>
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-ink-800 bg-ink-900/30 p-5"><p class="text-gray-400"><strong class="text-white">📋 Illegible handwriting</strong> — You can't enforce a waiver you can't read. Digital forms require complete, legible answers before submission.</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SOLUTION -->
  <section class="border-t border-ink-800/50 py-16">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white text-center">Digital Waivers That Work the Way Your Studio Does</h2>
      <div class="mt-12 space-y-16">
        <div class="grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-2 items-center">
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">QR Code Check-In</h3>
            <p class="mt-4 text-gray-400">Clients scan a QR code at the front desk, fill out the waiver on their phone, and you're ready. No shared devices, no cleaning screens between clients. Returning clients skip straight to consent — their info is already stored.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-xl bg-ink-900/50 border border-ink-800 p-8 text-center">
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">[Screenshot: QR check-in]</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-2 items-center">
          <div class="order-2 md:order-1 rounded-xl bg-ink-900/50 border border-ink-800 p-8 text-center">
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">[Screenshot: Medical history form]</p>
          </div>
          <div class="order-1 md:order-2">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">Smart Medical History</h3>
            <p class="mt-4 text-gray-400">Conditional logic adapts questions based on previous answers. Flag allergies, medications, and health conditions automatically. Each visit updates the record — complete history at your fingertips.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-2 items-center">
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">Legally Binding E-Signatures</h3>
            <p class="mt-4 text-gray-400">Every signature is timestamped and IP-logged. Compliant with ESIGN (US), UETA, and GDPR. Export any waiver as PDF for your records or health department audits.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-xl bg-ink-900/50 border border-ink-800 p-8 text-center">
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">[Screenshot: Signed waiver]</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- COMPARISON: InkFlow vs standalone waiver apps -->
  <section class="border-t border-ink-800/50 py-16 bg-ink-900/20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white text-center">InkFlow vs Standalone Waiver Apps</h2>
      <p class="mt-3 text-center text-gray-500">Dedicated waiver apps (Waiverly, Smartwaiver) only do waivers. InkFlow includes waivers <strong class="text-white">plus</strong> your entire studio workflow.</p>
      <div class="mt-8 space-y-3">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3"><div class="mt-1 flex h-6 w-6 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-accent-500/20"><span class="text-sm text-accent-400">✓</span></div><div><p class="text-white font-medium">Waiver + booking in one flow</p><p class="text-sm text-gray-400">Waivers generate from the appointment. No manual data entry between two systems.</p></div></div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3"><div class="mt-1 flex h-6 w-6 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-accent-500/20"><span class="text-sm text-accent-400">✓</span></div><div><p class="text-white font-medium">Client history attached to waivers</p><p class="text-sm text-gray-400">Every waiver links to the client's profile — past work, photos, payments. One place to look.</p></div></div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3"><div class="mt-1 flex h-6 w-6 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-accent-500/20"><span class="text-sm text-accent-400">✓</span></div><div><p class="text-white font-medium">No extra monthly fee for waivers</p><p class="text-sm text-gray-400">Waiverly costs $15-80/mo extra. InkFlow includes unlimited digital waivers in all plans.</p></div></div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3"><div class="mt-1 flex h-6 w-6 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-accent-500/20"><span class="text-sm text-accent-400">✓</span></div><div><p class="text-white font-medium">One login for your whole team</p><p class="text-sm text-gray-400">Artists, front desk, owner — all in one system. No switching between apps.</p></div></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- BUYER'S CHECKLIST -->
  <section class="border-t border-ink-800/50 py-16">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="mb-4 text-2xl font-bold text-white">What to Look For in a Digital Waiver App</h2>
      <p class="mb-6 text-gray-400">Not all digital waiver apps are created equal. Here's what matters:</p>
      <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-400">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="mt-1 text-accent-400">✓</span> <strong class="text-white">Legally binding e-signatures</strong> — Timestamps + IP log, ESIGN/UETA compliant</li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="mt-1 text-accent-400">✓</span> <strong class="text-white">Conditional logic</strong> — Questions adapt based on client answers</li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="mt-1 text-accent-400">✓</span> <strong class="text-white">PDF export</strong> — For legal records and health department audits</li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="mt-1 text-accent-400">✓</span> <strong class="text-white">QR code check-in</strong> — Touchless intake, available 24/7</li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="mt-1 text-accent-400">✓</span> <strong class="text-white">Parental consent workflows</strong> — Minor clients need separate flows</li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="mt-1 text-accent-400">✓</span> <strong class="text-white">Integration with booking</strong> — Waivers should auto-generate from appointments</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ -->
  <section class="border-t border-ink-800/50 py-16">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 space-y-4">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white text-center">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
      <details class="rounded-xl border border-ink-800 p-4">
        <summary class="cursor-pointer text-sm font-medium text-white">Are digital waivers legally binding?</summary>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-400">Yes. E-signatures with timestamps + IP logging are binding under ESIGN (US), UETA, and GDPR. InkFlow stores every waiver with a full audit trail.</p>
      </details>
      <details class="rounded-xl border border-ink-800 p-4">
        <summary class="cursor-pointer text-sm font-medium text-white">Can clients sign on their own phone before arriving?</summary>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-400">Yes. Send a link in the booking confirmation or display a QR code at the door. Clients complete the waiver on their phone before they walk in.</p>
      </details>
      <details class="rounded-xl border border-ink-800 p-4">
        <summary class="cursor-pointer text-sm font-medium text-white">How is InkFlow different from Waiverly or Smartwaiver?</summary>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-400">Those are standalone waiver apps. InkFlow includes waivers, booking, payments, CRM, and aftercare in one platform — no integrations, no extra monthly fees.</p>
      </details>
      <details class="rounded-xl border border-ink-800 p-4">
        <summary class="cursor-pointer text-sm font-medium text-white">Do you have parental consent forms for minors?</summary>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-400">Yes. Built-in parental consent workflow. Minors' waivers require a guardian's e-signature and are stored separately for compliance.</p>
      </details>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="border-t border-ink-800/50 py-16 text-center">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">Go Paperless Today</h2>
    <p class="mt-3 text-gray-400">Start free. Set up your first digital waiver in 5 minutes.</p>
    <a href="https://app.ink-flows.com/register" class="mt-6 inline-block rounded-lg bg-accent-500 px-8 py-3.5 text-base font-semibold text-ink-950 hover:bg-accent-400 transition-all">Try InkFlow Free →</a>
    <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-gray-600"><a href="/blog/how-to-digitize-tattoo-waivers" class="text-accent-400 hover:underline">Read: How to Digitize Tattoo Waivers →</a></p>
  </section>

  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>
